Author: HappierHungry
Text: I always sign up for over-priced gym classes/programs/'30 day challenges' during that "oh fuck, what have I done?" stage post-binge, particularly now that I'm trying my best not to purge... haha yeah, I'm definitely not the epitome of health, but there are people who insist on doing the whole "omg you're sooo good..." haaa
